The kidney matrisome in health, aging and disease.
Coupled with single cell transcriptomics there is the potential to identify the cellular origin of matrix changes, which could enable cell targeted therapy. This review provides a contemporary perspective of the complex kidney matrisome and draws comparison to altered matrix in heart and liver disease.
